Link</span>\n                <h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold cursor-pointer hover:text-blue-500 transition-colors\" onclick=\"navigator.clipboard.writeText('TP-Link Archer AX55')\">Archer AX55</h2>\n                <div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 pt-2 border-t border-slate-100 dark:border-[#1e2d45]\">\n                    <span class=\"text-xs font-semibold py-1 px-2 bg-green-100 text-green-700 dark:bg-[#062016] dark:text-[#4ade80] rounded\">Qualcomm Dual-Core</span>\n                    <span class=\"text-xs font-semibold py-1 px-2 bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 dark:bg-[#2d1f06] dark:text-[#f59e0b] rounded\">USB 3.0</span>\n                </div>\n                <p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-[#94a3b8] leading-snug pt-2\">الخيار المثالي للمكاتب المنزلية والعمل الذي يتطلب استقراراً عالياً بفضل معالج كوالكوم.</p>\n                <div class=\"text-xl font-black text-blue-600 dark:text-[#0ea5e9] pt-4\">95,000 د.ع</div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-[#111827] rounded-2xl border-2 border-orange-500 dark:border-orange-600 p-5 shadow-xl relative group\">\n            <div class=\"absolute -top-3 right-6 bg-orange-500 text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full shadow-lg\">الأقوى تغطية 🏆</div>\n            <div class=\"h-44 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-[#1a2235] rounded-xl p-4\">\n                <img src=\"https://singapore-1312056779.cos.accelerate.myqcloud.com/background/other/2023-07-13/42513a2a1d5d4e07a1e272867aedb424.png\" alt=\"Ruijie EW3000GX PRO\" class=\"max-h-full object-contain group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"space-y-3\">\n                <span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold text-orange-500 uppercase tracking-wider\">Ruijie</span>\n                <h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold cursor-pointer hover:text-orange-500 transition-colors\" onclick=\"navigator.clipboard.writeText('Ruijie EW3000GX PRO')\"