an>\n                    <span class=\"text-xs font-semibold py-1 px-2 bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 dark:bg-[#0c2a3e] dark:text-[#38bdf8] rounded\">NFC One-Hop</span>\n                </div>\n                <p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-[#94a3b8] leading-snug pt-2\">الأقوى في معالجة البيانات وتعدد الأجهزة؛ بفضل المعالج رباعي النواة الجبار.</p>\n                <div class=\"text-xl font-black text-emerald-600 dark:text-[#4ade80] pt-4\">85,000 د.ع</div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-[#111827] rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-[#1e2d45] p-5 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 group overflow-hidden\">\n            <div class=\"h-44 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-[#1a2235] rounded-xl p-4\">\n                <img src=\"https://i01.appmifile.com/webfile/globalimg/songxinyu/product/xiaomi-router-ax3200.png\" alt=\"Xiaomi AX3200\" class=\"max-h-full object-contain group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"space-y-3\">\n                <span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold text-pink-500 uppercase tracking-wider\">Xiaomi</span>\n                <h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold cursor-pointer hover:text-pink-500 transition-colors\" onclick=\"navigator.clipboard.writeText('Xiaomi AX3200')\">AX3200</h2>\n                <div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 pt-2 border-t border-slate-100 dark:border-[#1e2d45]\">\n                    <span class=\"text-xs font-semibold py-1 px-2 bg-pink-100 text-pink-700 dark:bg-[#3a1a3a] dark:text-[#e879f9] rounded\">3200 Mbps</span>\n                    <span class=\"text-xs font-semibold py-1 px-2 bg-slate-100 text-slate-700 dark:bg-[#1a2235] dark:text-[#94a3b8] rounded\">6 Antennas</span>\n                </div>\n                <p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-[#94a3b8] leading-snug pt-2\">يمنحك أعلى سرعة خام مع 6 هوائيات توزيع؛ مناسب جداً لمشاهدة الأفلام بدقة 4K.</p>\n                <div class=\"text-xl font-black text-pink-600 dark:text-[#e879f9] pt-4\">90,000 د.ع</div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-[#111827] rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-[#1e2d45] p-5 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 group overflow-hidden\">\n            <div class=\"h-44 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-[#1a2235] rounded-xl p-4\">\n                <img src=\"https://static.tp-link.com/upload/image-line/Overview_AX53_02_normal_20211209063348h.jpg\" alt=\"Archer AX53\" class=\"max-h-full object-contain group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"space-y-3\">\n                <span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold text-blue-500 uppercase tracking-wider\">TP-Link</span>\n                <h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold cursor-pointer hover:text-blue-500 transition-colors\" onclick=\"navigator.clipboard.writeText('TP-Link Archer AX53')\">Archer AX53</h2>\n                <div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 pt-2 border-t border-slate-100 dark:border-[#1e2d45]\">\n                    <span class=\"text-xs font-semibold py-1 px-2 bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 dark:bg-[#0c2a3e] dark:text-[#38bdf8] rounded\">HomeShield</span>\n                    <span class=\"text-xs font-semibold py-1 px-2 bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 dark:bg-[#2d1f06] dark:text-[#f59e0b] rounded\">WiFi 6</span>\n                </div>\n                <p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-[#94a3b8] leading-snug pt-2\">الأخ الأصغر لـ AX55، يوفر نفس تقنية WiFi 6 المتطورة وبسعر أكثر اقتصادية.</p>\n                <div class=\"text-xl font-black text-blue-600 dark:text-[#0ea5e9] pt-4\">85,000 د.ع</div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-blue-600 dark:bg-[#0ea5e9]/10 border-r-8 border-blue-400 dark:border-[#0ea5e9] p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl\">\n        <h3 class=\"text-white dark:text-[#0ea5e9] text-2xl font-black mb-6 flex items-center gap-3\">\n            <span>💡</span> كيف تختار الراوتر المناسب لك؟\n        </h3>\n        <ul class=\"space-y-4 text-white/90 dark:text-[#f1f5f9] text-sm md:text-base\">\n            <li class=\"flex items-center gap-4 bg-white/10 p-3 rounded-lg\">\n                <span class=\"bg-white/20 px-3 py-1 rounded font-bold\">للتغطية</span>\n                <span>اختر <strong class=\"text-orange-300\">Ruijie EW3000GX PRO</strong> (بيوت مساحة 200م فأكثر).</span>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"flex items-center gap-4 bg-white/10 p-3 rounded-lg\">\n                <span class=\"bg-white/20 px-3 py-1 rounded font-bold\">للألعاب</span>\n                <span>اختر <strong class=\"text-blue-300\">TP-Link Archer AX55</strong> (استقرار البنك والاتصال).</span>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"flex items-center gap-4 bg-white/10 p-3 rounded-lg\">\n                <span class=\"bg-white/20 px-3 py-1 rounded font-bold\">للعائلات</span>\n                <span>اختر <strong class=\"text-emerald-300\">Huawei AX3 Quad-Core</strong> (تعدد الأجهزة المتصلة).</span>\n            </li>\n        </ul>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto mt-16 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-6 border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-[#1e2d45] pt-10 text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 dark:text-[#475569]\">\n        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\">\n            <p>© 2026 دليل KINANTOUCH التقني</p>\n            <span class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-green-500 rounded-full\"></span>\n            <p>البيانات محدثة وفقاً للسوق المحلي</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"flex gap-4\">\n            <span class=\"hover:text-blue-500 cursor-help transition-colors\">دليل الشبكات</span>\n            <span class=\"hover:text-blue-500 cursor-help transition-colors\">استشارات فنية</span>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n</div>",
